# xoxo

Balanced diversity solver xoxo to the square.

[License: MIT](https://git.sr.ht/~sthagen/xoxo/tree/default/item/LICENSE)

[![version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/xoxo.svg?style=flat)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/xoxo/)
